com.kt.ca
Interface CAEventListener

public interface CAEventListener

CAEventListener is interested in CA event. The implementing class is supposed to handle CA event and do nothing for uninterested CA event.

NOTE: Refers KT-CAS API document for the detail message format and tag value.
